cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.SI 

This paper is about traitor tracing schemes, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses code constructions and analysis, which are topics in information theory (cs.IT) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper may also be relevant to the field of coding theory (cs.CC) and possibly to the subfield of signal processing (cs.SI) due to the use of distribution functions and score functions.
